Why does it have to be so simple? Because you want it to be...I think lots of religious people are like that, they want a quick, succinct, all-encompassing answer to where we came from, what are we doing here, and what happens to us after we die. Sorry things can't be explained so easily for you. Try opening a   science   book and actually learning about what few things we have managed to understand about the universe. I'm sure it's just scratching the surface.